ucture. We provide new\nconstraints to the binary neutron star merger rates of\n$1{-}1300$Gpc$^{-3}$yr$^{-1}$ or $2{-}680$Gpc$^{-3}$yr$^{-1}$ when a fitted\nluminosity function is assumed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2023 16:07:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 09:27:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
